quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,Ndi pali nyenyezi pamene ili kulowa
  53,2,M’bale wanu sadasochere kapena kuti ndi wolakwa
  53,3,Ndipo iye sayankhula zofuna zake
  53,4,Icho ndi chochita kuuzidwa kwa iye
  53,5,Iye adaphunzitsidwa ndi Iye amene ali ndi mphamvu
  53,6,"Wopanda chilema chilichonse, kotero adadzuka ndi kukhala wokhazikika"
  53,7,Pamene iye anali patali kwambiri mu mlengalenga
  53,8,Ndipo adasendera ndi kudza pafupi
  53,9,Ndipo adali pa mtunda wolingana kuponya mipaliro iwiri kapena kucheperapo
  53,10,Motero Iye adaulula Uthenga kwa kapolo wake kudzera mwa Gabriyele
  53,11,Mtima wake wa Mtumwi siudaname ponena zimene iye adaona
  53,12,Kodi inu mudzatsutsana naye pa zimene iye adaona
  53,13,Ndithudi iye adamuona iye pamene anali kutsika kachiwiri
  53,14,Pafupi ndi mtengo wa Sidrah
  53,15,Pafupi pake pali munda womwe ndi malo opumirako
  53,16,Ndipo chimene chimaphimba chidakuta mtengo wa Sidrah
  53,17,Maso ake sadayang’ane kumbali kapena kupyola muyeso
  53,18,Ndithudi iye adaona zizindikiro zazikulu kwambiri za Ambuye wake
  53,19,Kodi inu maganiza za Lat ndi Uzza
  53,20,Ndi Manat wachitatu wamkazi
  53,21,Kwa inu amuna ndipo kwa Iye akazi
  53,22,Ndithudi kumeneku ndiko kugawa kosalungama
  53,23,"Awa ndi mayina chabe amene inu mwapeka, inu ndi atate anu, amene Mulungu sadakulamuleni ndi pang’ono pomwe. Iwo amangotsatira nkhani zakumva chabe zimene mitima yawo imafuna pamene, ndithudi, kwadza kale kwa iwo ulangizi wochokera kwa Ambuye wawo"
  53,24,Kodi munthu angapeze zonse zimene amafuna
  53,25,Koma Mulungu ndiye Mwini moyo umene uli nkudza ndi moyo wakale
  53,26,Ndipo kuli angelo ambiri amene ali kumwamba amene kukhala pakati kwawo sikudzathandiza chilichonse kupatula pokhapo pamene Mulungu apereka chilolezo kwa amene Iye wamufuna ndi kukondweretsedwa naye
  53,27,"Ndithudi iwo amene sakhulupirira za m’moyo umene uli nkudza, amatcha angelo ndi mayina achikazi"
  53,28,"Pamene iwo sadziwa chilichonse cha izo. Iwo satsatira china chilichonse koma nkhani zabodza ndipo, ndithudi, nkhani zabodza si mlowam’malo wa choonadi"
  53,29,Motero mupewe wina aliyense amene salabadira chikumbutso chathu ndipo safuna china chilichonse koma moyo wa padziko lino lapansi
  53,30,Uko ndiko kuchuluka kwa nzeru zawo. Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndiye amadziwa bwino onse amene amasochera ku njira yoyenera ndipo amadziwa kwambiri iye amene amatsata njira yoyenera
  53,31,"Ndipo Mulungu ndiye mwini wake wa chilichonse chimene chili kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, ndipo akhoza kulanga onse amene amachita zoipa molingana ndi ntchito zawo ndiponso kuti akhoza kulipira onse amene amachita zabwino ndi mphotho yabwino kwambiri"
  53,32,"Iwo amene amapewa machimo a akuluakulu ndi chigololo kupatula machimo a ang’onoang’ono, ndithudi, Ambuye wako ndi Mwini chikhululukiro. Iye amakudziwani bwino pamene amakulengani kuchokera ku dothi ndi pamene mukutidwa m’mimba mwa amayi anu. Motero musadziyeretse nokha. Al Najm\t567 Iye amadziwa bwino kwambiri aliyense amene amalewa zoipa"
  53,33,Kodi iwe wamuona amene amabwerera m’mbuyo
  53,34,Amene adapereka pang’ono ndipo anasiya kupereka
  53,35,Kodi iye amadziwa za zinthu zobisika kuti akhoza kuziona
  53,36,Kodi kapena iye sadauzidwe za mawu amene ali m’mabuku a Mose
  53,37,Ndiponso za Abrahamu amene adakwaniritsa malamulo
  53,38,Kuti palibe munthu amene adzasenza katundu wa mnzake
  53,39,Ndipo kuti munthu sadzapeza chilichonse kupatula chimene wachigwirira ntchito
  53,40,Ndipo kuti ntchito zake zidzaoneka
  53,41,Pamenepo iye adzalipidwa malipiro ake oyenera
  53,42,Ndipo kuti kwa Ambuye wanu ndi kumene nonse mudzapita
  53,43,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amawachititsa anthu kuseka ndi kuwaliritsa
  53,44,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amapereka imfa ndi moyo
  53,45,"Ndiponso kuti Iye adalenga zinthu ziwiriziwiri, chachimuna ndi chachikazi"
  53,46,Kuchokera ku madontho a umuna umene umatuluka
  53,47,Ndipo kuti kwa Iye kuli chilengedwe chachiwiri
  53,48,Ndipo kuti Ndiye amene amapereka chuma ndi chisangalalo
  53,49,Ndipo kuti Iye ndiye Ambuye wa nyenyezi yamphamvu yotchedwa Sirius
  53,50,Kuti ndiye amene adaononga anthu akale a mphamvu kwambiri a mtundu wa a Aad kale
  53,51,Ndi anthu a mtundu wa a Thamoud. Ndipo Iye sadasiye wina aliyense
  53,52,Ndi anthu a Nowa amakedzana ndithudi iwo adali osalungama ndi oswa malamulo mwamwano
  53,53,Ndipo iye adaononga mizinda yomwe idali yogonjetsedwa
  53,54,Kotero iwo adawavundikira nd chimene chidawavundikira
  53,55,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wako zimene udzazikayikira
  53,56,Uyu ndi mchenjezi wotsatizana ndi achenjezi a makedzana
  53,57,Tsiku louka kwa akufa lili pafupi
  53,58,Palibe wina kupatula Mulungu amene akhoza kulipherera
  53,59,Kodi inu mulikudabwa pa zimene zili kulakatulidwa
  53,60,Ndipo inu muli kuseka m’malo mwakulira
  53,61,Ndi kumapitirizabe kuchita zinthu zopanda pake
  53,62,Motero gunditsani nkhope zanu pansi ndipo pembedzani Mulungu mmodzi yekha